comments: Jones (SAS) legally contests Jones' (WAS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Kuzma (WAS) is moving alongside Wembanyama's (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs in the post.
Kispert (WAS) jumps slightly forward towards Jones (SAS) and marginal contact occurs with Jones' slightly extended left forearm.
Wembanyama (SAS) extends his leg out and makes intentional foot to ball contact.
Wembanyama (SAS) cleanly blocks Jones' (WAS) shot attempt prior to the ball making contact with the backboard.
Vassell (SAS) releases away from Coulibaly (WAS), and the contact on the perimeter is marginal.
Wembanyama (SAS) is already in Bagley III's (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs to his slightly extended left arm.
Wembanyama (SAS) cleanly blocks Jones' (WAS) shot attempt before the ball touches the backboard.
Wembanyama (SAS) initiates contact with Bagley III's (WAS) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Bagley III (WAS) moves laterally into Sochan's (SAS) path and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Sochan (SAS) moves alongside Kuzma's (WAS) path and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Bagley III (WAS) and Wembanyama (SAS) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Poole (WAS) commits a take foul on Jones (SAS).
Sochan (SAS) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Poole (WAS) commits a take foul on Vassell (SAS).
Bagley III (WAS) briefly grasps Wembanyama's (SAS) right arm and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
Sochan (SAS) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Kispert (WAS) and, as he is landing ,cleanly dislodges the ball during his contest on the jump shot attempt.
